9. put yourself first! stay hydrated and break the fast if you feel too lightheaded or dizzy. you’re way more important than a few extra hours of not eating ♡

8. break the fast with light foods like raw fruits and vegetables, broth, or yogurt. <3 breaking a fast with foods with high carbohydrates or sugar can upset your stomach and cause headaches!
7. don’t overexercise! exercising too much while fasting can lead to muscle breakdown and exhaustion! stick to a light walk, cardio, or yoga ^^
6. work up your hours! if you haven’t fasted before or try to fast for much longer than you’ve tried before, it’s likely to end in a binge. try to fast a couple hours extra each time ♡

5. stay motivated! ^^ making a pinterest board of cute clothes or looking at thinspo (if that personally motivate you) can help <3 remind yourself why you started your fast and keep track of your progress!
4. track track track! using apps to track your fast and journaling the process can help you keep note of how you’re feeling and also help you to stay motivated <3
